{"tid":710381,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星 岩先同個健身sale吵大鑊 發現大隻佬都係不外如事","createTime":"2018-06-20T16:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T17:30:25.000Z","uid":54581,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"076f9493d8ba452706209a1751c09fe2110f27aa","tid":710381,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"岩先行街 條友拉我手臂話我咁瘦不如做gym 操起佢<br />\n<br />\n屌那星 佢個野鏈落黎 成個手臂都係個五個手指印<br />\n<br />\n我都已經夠有品 心諗 忍讓下 百忍成金<br />\n<br />\n點知我掉轉頭諗住走 佢一野扯番我轉頭 仲chok親個膊頭 勁響咁啪左聲 條頸都扭親下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我咪屌鳩佢：你可唔可以唔好咁大力 <br />\n再指住我隻手個手指印 落佢臉<br />\n<br />\n佢當然向我道歉 say晒梳咁<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就黑晒臉走左去R第個客<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢走都要撞我一野 痛撚到依家<br />\n但無計，啲人低eq就係咁<br />\n<br />\n我都無謂同佢理論咁多<br />\n<br />\nChip 一聲就走左<br />\n<br />\n佢都知佢理虧，唔夠膽同我嘈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挑 大隻仔，不外如事"},{"pid":"f2f1012ecbea5089df0bb7011fd31a6cf9936d44","tid":710381,"uid":14602,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"樓豬好廢，俾著我一拳打到佢入ICU"},{"pid":"78c2c90514f7f5c77fc02b57d54049da2f936d23","tid":710381,"uid":54417,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"窮尻毒撚聲稱大戰健身sale狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a5d02916952cc344f8c36a4a72665644b78c8c","tid":710381,"uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"佢有冇腹肌"},{"pid":"fabe70654161f7ba4baf124933c6d8d9a80964e2","tid":710381,"uid":54417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">瘦</span>尻毒撚聲稱大戰健身sale狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 